{"id":78241,"type":6,"name":"Beauty and the Beast Season 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/de/f7/78241_NlNtx.jpg","rating":{"total":3,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":0,"8":1,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.3},"summary":"本剧由CW制作，翻拍自80年代明同名剧集《侠胆雄狮》（Beauty and the Beast），新版的时代背景会更加具有现代感。 \r\n19岁的Catherine（克斯汀·克鲁克 Kristin Kreuk 饰）亲眼目睹了母亲惨死，自己则在神秘物种的帮助下逃过一劫。多年后她当上了调查谋杀案的女警官。在调查某一起谋杀案时，其中一条线索将她引向了早该死于阿富汗的医生Vincent（杰.瑞恩 Jay Ryan 饰）。随着对案件的追查，她渐渐了解了真相：Vincent就是她的救命恩人，因被注射某种药物而变成了一个半兽人，在被激怒时候会变成野兽。Catherine答应Vincent为其保守秘密，但他必须要告诉她关于母亲之死的线索。从此开始，两人之间复杂的关系开始萌芽，即相互吸引，彼此却又心知肚明这样的关系只会给两个人带来危险......","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>新侠胆雄狮 第一季</li><li><span>集数: </span>22</li><li><span>开始: </span>2012-10-11</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 爱情 / 犯罪</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>42 分钟</li><li><span>电视台: </span>CW</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>www.cwtv.com/shows/beauty-and-the-beast</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt2193041</li>","collection":{"collect":2,"doing":2,"on_hold":3,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"2012","count":1},{"name":"美剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":296861,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296861","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":296862,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296862","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":296863,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296863","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":296864,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296864","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":296865,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296865","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":296866,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296866","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","st